<div id="txtcont" class="span9" style="position: relative;">
    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='155:181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-1a' );" name="011-1a" class="pb">[011-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='181:189'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='189:198'>　詩總聞卷十一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='198:218'>　　　　　　　　　　　　宋　王質　撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='218:224'>　　鴻鴈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='224:231'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='231:241'>鴻鴈于飛肅肅其羽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='241:264'>　西北鴻鴈来正月節此詩當是春來鴻鴈初歸故鄉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='264:281'>　新棲未定舊迹已湮故曰哀鳴嗷嗷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='281:307'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-1b' );" name="011-1b" class="pb">[011-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='307:325'>之子于征劬勞于野爰及矜人哀此鰥寡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='325:348'>　當是授民以田也最可憐者孤獨鰥寡之人人而重</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='348:371'>　可哀者鰥寡之人也老而無子尚可養旁親為義子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='371:394'>　㓜而無父尚可依他族為義父惟老而無妻無復更</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='394:414'>　娶老而無夫無復更嫁終身永已故可哀也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='414:421'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='421:444'>鴻鴈于飛集于中澤之子于垣百堵皆作雖則劬勞其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='444:449'>究安宅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='449:475'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-2a' );" name="011-2a" class="pb">[011-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='475:497'>　當是授民以舎也雖勞畢事則歸家自解之辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='497:504'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='504:527'>鴻鴈于飛哀鳴嗷嗷維此哲人謂我劬勞維彼愚人謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='527:532'>我宣驕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='532:555'>　哲人暢于人情憫我之勞也愚人暗于物理謂我為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='555:578'>　民任勞示之以驕將不可令也大率一種無識者謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='578:601'>　百姓不足顧恤顧恤則頑肆惟有事則深懲無事則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='601:624'>　勿顧則民知畏而易馭彼以為有術有能而不自知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='624:650'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-2b' );" name="011-2b" class="pb">[011-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='650:657'>　其真愚也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='657:680'>　　聞音曰野上與切寡果五切澤徒洛切宅逹各切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='680:703'>　　　班氏陳湯傳斬越毒鼔顔氏西域傳作毋寡此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='703:726'>　　　作毋鼓聲相近夷狄之音不甚諦也此音至漢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='726:749'>　　　猶存至唐已不傳矣鄭氏縫人注引書宅西曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='749:772'>　　　昧谷作度西曰栁糓陸氏古文宅與度相近因</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='772:795'>　　　此而誤此音至漢亦存至唐又不傳也大率古</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='795:814'>　　　音漸逺漸轉而况愈逺今併載於此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='814:840'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-3a' );" name="011-3a" class="pb">[011-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='840:863'>總聞曰此士大夫將王命而定民所者也三章劬勞皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='863:886'>士大夫自謂恐難獨以中章為勸民之辭女今雖病勞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='886:901'>終有安居此意甚佳但語勢不爾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='901:907'>　　庭燎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='907:914'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='914:935'>夜如何其夜未央庭燎之光君子至止鸞聲將將</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='935:942'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='942:963'>夜如何其夜未艾庭燎晰晰君子至止鸞聲噦噦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='963:989'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-3b' );" name="011-3b" class="pb">[011-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='989:996'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='996:1017'>夜如何其夜鄉晨庭燎有煇君子至止言觀其旂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1017:1040'>　　聞音曰將七羊切艾魚肺切晰之逝切煇許云切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1040:1049'>　　　旂渠斤切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1049:1072'>總聞曰鄭氏宣王問早晚之辭人君數問夜亦非體此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1072:1095'>當是執事之人夜未央未艾而聞車音夜鄉晨而見旂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1095:1118'>色嘆夜漏之未盡而朝臣之已集也所謂不圖今日復</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1118:1141'>見漢官威儀乆不接耳目驟以為驚且為喜也恐是殿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1141:1167'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-4a' );" name="011-4a" class="pb">[011-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1167:1190'>庭之間宫掖之内執事者相與問答之辭也禮雞人夜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1190:1213'>呼旦以驚百官漢儀中黄門持五夜甲乙丙丁戊相傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1213:1231'>朱明衛士起唱所謂雞鳴歌也或是此曹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1231:1237'>　　沔水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1237:1244'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1244:1267'>沔彼流水朝宗于海鴥彼飛隼載飛載止嗟我兄弟邦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1267:1280'>人諸友莫肯念亂誰無父母</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1280:1287'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1287:1313'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-4b' );" name="011-4b" class="pb">[011-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1313:1336'>沔彼流水其流湯湯鴥彼飛隼載飛載揚念彼不蹟載</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1336:1349'>起載行心之憂矣不可弭忘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1349:1372'>　屈氏歩徙倚而遥思怊惝恍而永懐意荒蕩而流蕩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1372:1395'>　心愁悽而轉悲言不循法度之人而反以我為此流</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1395:1418'>　故懐憂如此鄭氏以起行為妄興師出兵事實既不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1418:1435'>　然人情亦不爾若此詩人之情喪也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1435:1442'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1442:1465'>鴥彼飛隼率彼中陵民之訛言寜莫之懲我友敬矣䜛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1465:1491'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-5a' );" name="011-5a" class="pb">[011-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1491:1496'>言其興</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1496:1519'>　陳氏闕沔彼流水云八字亦精考者然不必如此前</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1519:1542'>　二章見隼止沔水之旁後一章見隼循中陵之上當</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1542:1562'>　是中陵與沔水異塗各道所見不必相同也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1562:1585'>　　聞音曰海虎猥切友羽軌切毋滿罪切湯失羊切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1585:1594'>　　　行户郎切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1594:1614'>　　聞跡曰沔水出武都沮縣毛氏流滿未考</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1614:1637'>總聞曰當是關輔諸侯有來朝後時者興下之䜛致上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1637:1663'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-5b' );" name="011-5b" class="pb">[011-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1663:1686'>之疑徃時固有亂者固有不蹟者今誰念之而効之乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1686:1709'>皆由訛言不懲故懐敬君之心得慢君之咎有此䜛也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1709:1732'>見順流之水自適之禽而嘆其不如是必其䜛已就欲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1732:1755'>見而不敢見慮蹈禍也此或為其友愬䜛者故曰我友</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1755:1763'>敬矣䜛言其興</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1763:1769'>　　鶴鳴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1769:1776'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1776:1795'>鶴鳴于九臯聲聞于野魚濳在淵或在于渚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1795:1821'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-6a' );" name="011-6a" class="pb">[011-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1821:1828'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='1828:1850'>樂彼之園爰有樹檀其下維蘀他山之石可以為錯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='1850:1873'>　澤玩鶴水玩魚言賢者退處自樂也不惟如此而園</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='1873:1896'>　有檀可以為器其墮葉亦可以代薪其穀菜亦可以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='1896:1918'>　為茹山有石亦可以為礪取用何闕所以為樂也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='1918:1925'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='1925:1944'>鶴鳴于九臯聲聞于天魚在于渚或濳在淵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='1944:1951'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='1951:1977'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-6b' );" name="011-6b" class="pb">[011-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='1977:1999'>樂彼之園爰有樹檀其下維穀他山之石可以攻玉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='1999:2022'>　　聞音曰野上與切檀徒泫切天淵從今音不必作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2022:2045'>　　　鐡因一均詩用天二十三用淵六雖無叶他年</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2045:2066'>　　　縈年二切既叶亦可吳氏不必從一讀也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2066:2080'>　　聞章曰舊二章今為四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2080:2103'>　　聞物曰糓菜葉似王𤓰實若龍葵今山間多食</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2103:2126'>總聞曰清修隠逸之士多喜觀鶴亦多喜觀魚列子詹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2126:2147'>何莊子惠子之事可見載在傳記及見篇章甚多</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2147:2173'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-7a' );" name="011-7a" class="pb">[011-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2173:2179'>　　祈父</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2179:2186'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2186:2208'>祈父<span class='krp-note'>止/</span>予王之爪牙胡轉予于恤靡所止居</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2208:2231'>　此士卒怨將帥之辭也呼之以父而告之以情我于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2231:2254'>　王為爪牙衛國家者也何忍轉我于憂不安其居而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2254:2264'>　無所至怨之辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2264:2271'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2271:2293'>祈父<span class='krp-note'>止/</span>予王之爪士胡轉予于恤靡所底止</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2293:2319'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-7b' );" name="011-7b" class="pb">[011-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2319:2326'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2326:2347'>祈父<span class='krp-note'>止/</span>亶不聰胡轉予于恤有母之尸饔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2347:2353'>　　白駒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2353:2360'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2360:2383'>皎皎白駒食我場苗縶之維之以永今朝所謂伊人於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2383:2388'>焉逍遥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2388:2395'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2395:2418'>皎皎白駒食我埸藿縶之維之以永今夕所謂伊人於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2418:2444'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-8a' );" name="011-8a" class="pb">[011-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2444:2449'>焉嘉客</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2449:2456'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2456:2479'>皎皎白駒賁然來思爾公爾侯逸豫無期慎爾優㳺勉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2479:2484'>爾遁思</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2484:2507'>　此必舊為公侯而今遁山林者也度斯人浪適其來</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2507:2525'>　無期少寄丁寜頌禱之辭愛賢之深也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2525:2532'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2532:2555'>皎皎白駒在彼空谷生芻一束其人如玉毋金玉爾音</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='2555:2581'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-8b' );" name="011-8b" class="pb">[011-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='2581:2587'>而有遐心</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='2587:2610'>　始猶兾白駒之來可以施謀今不復望知白駒終不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='2610:2633'>　出谷也猶欲寄生芻以秣白駒而又恐其人過潔雖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='2633:2656'>　芻亦不肯受也今相踈如此不可閟其音而與我絶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='2656:2676'>　有相逺之意也盖欲時通訊問以求善言也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='2676:2699'>　　聞音曰夕祥龠切客克各切古客皆讀如恪三恪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='2699:2722'>　　　即三客也孔叢子陳王問太師三恪曰封夏殷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='2722:2746'>　　　之後為二代紹虞帝之𦙍備三恪恪敬也禮之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='2746:2772'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-9a' );" name="011-9a" class="pb">[011-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='2772:2795'>　　　如賓客也客恪皆同楚辭易林古詩漢歌皆用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='2795:2805'>　　　此思新齎切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='2805:2828'>總聞曰此亦在野之賢者尚與世相通欲求道義為師</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='2828:2844'>友而所欲挽者又長徃而不返者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='2844:2850'>　　黄鳥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='2850:2857'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='2857:2880'>黄鳥黄鳥無集于穀無啄我粟此邦之人不我肯糓言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='2880:2889'>旋言歸復我邦族</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='2889:2915'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-9b' );" name="011-9b" class="pb">[011-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='2915:2938'>　此離散之餘去本邦而寓他土者也借黄鳥為辭無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='2938:2961'>　集我糓無啄我粟留為歸資復見舊族也厭他土而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='2961:2970'>　思本邦之辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='2970:2977'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='2977:3000'>黄鳥黄鳥無集于桑無啄我梁此邦之人不可與明言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3000:3009'>旋言歸復我諸兄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3009:3016'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3016:3039'>黄鳥黄鳥無集于栩無啄我黍此邦之人不可與處言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3039:3066'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-10a' );" name="011-10a" class="pb">[011-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3066:3075'>旋言歸復我諸父</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3075:3094'>　　聞音曰明謨良切兄虛王切父扶雨切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3094:3117'>　　聞訓曰無集于穀楮也不我肯糓善也上糓從木</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3117:3126'>　　　下糓從米</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3126:3149'>總聞曰當是為生異方必經多時種木植禾已成不復</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3149:3170'>戀而决舎去者此邦必有所不可留而非得已也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3170:3178'>　　我行其野</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3178:3185'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3185:3212'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-10b' );" name="011-10b" class="pb">[011-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3212:3235'>我行其野蔽芾其樗昏姻之故言就而居爾不我畜復</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3235:3240'>我邦家</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3240:3247'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3247:3270'>我行其野言采其蓫昏姻之故言就爾宿爾不我畜言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3270:3275'>歸斯復</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3275:3282'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3282:3305'>我行其野言采其葍不思舊姻求爾新特成不以富亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3305:3310'>祗以異</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='3310:3337'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-11a' );" name="011-11a" class="pb">[011-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='3337:3360'>　此以貧欲棄舊婚而以富欲求新匹者也雖成不足</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='3360:3383'>　以致富假使有得亦終散而不聚也適足以為怪言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='3383:3400'>　逐夫而適夫豈有此理也此皆婿辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='3400:3419'>　　聞音曰家古胡切葍筆力切異逸織切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='3419:3442'>　　聞物曰樗即楮也毛氏他氏皆但謂之惡木不言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='3442:3465'>　　　何木也樗楮相邇今俗傳雖薪亦不堪然皮可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='3465:3488'>　　　紙實可練葉可覆麴醬極易長茂蓫葍毛鄭皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='3488:3511'>　　　云惡菜鄭氏言蓫牛蘈菜也郭氏方莖莖長而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='3511:3538'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-11b' );" name="011-11b" class="pb">[011-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='3538:3561'>　　　鋭有穗有花花紫縹鄭氏葍䔰也爾雅蔓芽也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='3561:3584'>　　　郭氏葍大葉白花赤花為蔓初不言何物本草</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='3584:3607'>　　　陳氏引詩言采其蓫羊蹄草也許氏以蔓為葍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='3607:3630'>　　　一名蕣集韻丁氏蕣木槿也引詩顔如蕣英雖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='3630:3653'>　　　不引此然今木槿有白紫二種與郭氏正合人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='3653:3675'>　　　雖采但不見食耳當是西北與東南又不同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='3675:3698'>總聞曰觀此詩然後知前詩之所以不可處者也二詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='3698:3704'>當出一人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='3704:3731'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-12a' );" name="011-12a" class="pb">[011-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='3731:3737'>　　斯干</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='3737:3744'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='3744:3754'>秩秩斯干幽幽南山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='3754:3777'>　干幹也今言人命上下為支干故下言松竹也凡居</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='3777:3792'>　向南為正靣南山則坐北山也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='3792:3802'>如竹苞矣如松茂矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='3802:3813'>　言靣勢物色皆嘉也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='3813:3827'>兄及弟矣式相好矣無相猶矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='3827:3854'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-12b' );" name="011-12b" class="pb">[011-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='3854:3866'>　言門户氣象又皆嘉也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='3866:3873'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='3873:3895'>似續妣祖築室百堵西南其戸爰居爰處爰笑爰語</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='3895:3918'>　然後興功作室也似續生者之室也妣祖死者之室</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='3918:3941'>　也死户向西坐東也生户向南坐北也死者於此居</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='3941:3957'>　處生者於此笑語言各安其所也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='3957:3964'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='3964:3986'>約之閣閣椓之槖槖風雨攸除鳥鼠攸去君子攸芋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='3986:4013'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-13a' );" name="011-13a" class="pb">[011-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4013:4036'>　自此以下毎章結以君子芋有數訓平聲一草盛也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4036:4059'>　一大也仄聲草名也吳氏所引説文大葉實根駭人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4059:4082'>　故謂之芌王過切者乃從芌也於文象氣之舒若從</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='4082:4105'>　芋當作平聲于文象氣之平雖通用而有異意集韻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='4105:4128'>　撫芋通用荒胡切覆也大也有也用此為的鄭氏改</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='4128:4150'>　芋為憮亦不誤但不須變字爾去除皆當從平聲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='4150:4157'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='4157:4179'>如跂斯翼如矢斯棘如鳥斯革如翬斯飛君子攸躋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='4179:4206'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-13b' );" name="011-13b" class="pb">[011-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='4206:4213'>　　　五章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='4213:4236'>殖殖其庭有覺其楹噲噲其正噦噦其𡨕君子攸寜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='4236:4245'>　皆生者所享也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='4245:4252'>　　　六章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='4252:4275'>下筦上簟乃安斯寢乃寢乃興乃占我夢吉夢維何維</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='4275:4284'>熊維羆維虺維蛇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='4284:4295'>　居旣安則福可致也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='4295:4302'>　　　七章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='4302:4329'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-14a' );" name="011-14a" class="pb">[011-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='4329:4351'>大人占之維熊維羆男子之祥維虺維蛇女子之祥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='4351:4374'>　鄭氏熊羆在山陽之祥也虺蛇在穴陰之祥也此意</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='4374:4397'>　甚嘉而未盡凡物不蟄者属陽蟄者属陰虎以冬交</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='4397:4420'>　藉陰以成也蛇以夏交藉陽以成也床在高陽也而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='4420:4443'>　璋以水成濟以陰也地在下隂也而瓦以火成濟以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='4443:4466'>　陽也古人處事制法無不合理無羊之夢亦然魚陰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='4466:4489'>　也禾亦陰也魚非水則不生然附日影乃成禾非水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='4489:4512'>　則不生然向日色乃成盖同類也故夢魚占豐年旟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='4512:4539'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-14b' );" name="011-14b" class="pb">[011-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='4539:4562'>　鳥隼飛者陽類也然寒乃健旐龜蛇濳者陰類也然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='4562:4585'>　勢乃毒萬物無逃二氣之間故夢旟旐多室家盖隂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='4585:4608'>　陽相交男女乃孶也易曰天地絪緼萬物化醇男女</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='4608:4617'>　搆精萬物化生</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='4617:4624'>　　　八章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='4624:4647'>乃生男子載寢之牀載衣之裳載㺯之璋其泣喤喤朱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='4647:4656'>芾斯皇室家君王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='4656:4669'>　室家皆事君王言貴近也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='4669:4696'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-15a' );" name="011-15a" class="pb">[011-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='4696:4703'>　　　九章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='4703:4726'>乃生女子載寢之地載衣之禓載㺯之瓦無非無儀唯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='4726:4737'>酒食是議無父母詒罹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='4737:4760'>　男子願使為公卿女子乃不願使為后妃惟議酒食</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='4760:4783'>　所謂中饋也此事多詒父母之憂罕延門户之福有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='4783:4806'>　識士大夫所以不欲也鄭氏儀善也婦人無所專於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='4806:4829'>　家事有非非婦人也有善亦非婦人也此意亦嘉而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='4829:4845'>　未盡但不當彰是非之名于外爾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='4845:4872'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-15b' );" name="011-15b" class="pb">[011-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='4872:4895'>　　聞音曰苞補掫切茂莫口切好許厚切猶余救切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='4895:4918'>　　　户後五切草訖力切正諸盈切簟子禁切今人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='4918:4941'>　　　猶有此聲吳氏前二章皆用引韻此一章不用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='4941:4964'>　　　未詳盖未察此也寢千尋切夢彌登切蛇余支</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='4964:4978'>　　　切瓦危委切議魚覊切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='4978:5001'>　　聞章曰舊九章四章七句五章五句今畧如舊章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='5001:5011'>　　　而差移舊句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='5011:5034'>　　聞事曰四如言人功之敏也跂敏于足而若有翼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='5034:5061'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-16a' );" name="011-16a" class="pb">[011-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='5061:5084'>　　　者言如鳥也矢敏於逺而又敏於近棘讀作㦸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='5084:5107'>　　　鳥敏於羽而若有革言若獸也翬敏於躍而又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='5107:5130'>　　　敏於飛翬雉也飛一作蜚蜚如螟春秋秋有蜚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='5130:5153'>總聞曰此士大夫卜地作室者也以為王者無見無羊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='5153:5157'>倣此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='5157:5163'>　　無羊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='5163:5170'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='5170:5190'>誰謂爾無羊三百維群誰謂爾無牛九十其犉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='5190:5217'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-16b' );" name="011-16b" class="pb">[011-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='5217:5224'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='5224:5247'>爾羊來思其角濈濈爾牛來思其耳濕濕或降於阿或</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='5247:5256'>飲於池或寢或訛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='5256:5263'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='5263:5286'>爾牧來思何蓑何笠或負其餱三十維物爾牲則具爾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='5286:5299'>牧來思以薪以蒸以雌以雄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='5299:5322'>　第五句爾牲則具當移入第七句以薪以蒸下以薪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='5322:5345'>　蒸之葉為牛羊雌雄之食也羊以三數凡三百頭是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='5345:5372'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-17a' );" name="011-17a" class="pb">[011-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='5372:5395'>　羊群之數牛以十數凡九十頭是牛群之數三十之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='5395:5405'>　物此也盖應上數</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='5405:5412'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='5412:5434'>爾羊來思矜矜兢兢不騫不崩麾之以肱畢來既升</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='5434:5457'>　第二句矜矜兢兢下恐少爾牛來思一句羊小畜矜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='5457:5480'>　矜兢兢羊畏聳貌牛大畜不騫不崩牛堅重貌明兢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='5480:5493'>　兢下不騫上少爾牛一句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='5493:5500'>　　　五章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='5500:5527'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-17b' );" name="011-17b" class="pb">[011-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='5527:5550'>牧人乃夢衆維魚矣旐維旟矣大人占之衆維魚矣實</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='5550:5563'>維豐年旐維旟矣室家溱溱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='5563:5570'>　説見斯干</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='5570:5593'>　　聞音曰犉而純切濈莊立切池唐何切物㣲律切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='5593:5616'>　　　今猶有此音雄于陵切孔氏兆如山陵有夫出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='5616:5639'>　　　征而喪其雄繇辭皆韻又古讀雄與陵爲韻詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='5639:5662'>　　　正月無羊皆以雄韻陵韻蒸韻又張氏賓爵下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='5662:5685'>　　　華田鼠上騰牛哀虎變鯀化為熊乆血為燐積</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='5685:5712'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-18a' );" name="011-18a" class="pb">[011-18a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='5712:5735'>　　　灰生蝇或疑張氏王氐古讀熊與雄皆于陵切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='5735:5749'>　　　張用舊韻也年彌因切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='5749:5763'>　　聞章曰舊四章今為五章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='5763:5786'>　　聞字曰濈濈鋭貌正羊角之狀從角尤佳不從角</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='5786:5809'>　　　亦可説文和也毛氏息也似不必他訓牛安則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='5809:5832'>　　　耳潤病則耳燥濕濕牛安也毛氏動也訓亦似</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='5832:5855'>　　　未當羊以角言牛以耳言恐是當時降阿飲池</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='5855:5878'>　　　皆為水所沾後世不肯從物情時態推測古人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='5878:5905'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '011-18b' );" name="011-18b" class="pb">[011-18b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='5905:5928'>　　　簡易之意多以造意為能然古字亦通用斯干</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='5928:5949'>　　　于加草亦止是于意戢從水亦止是鋭意</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='5949:5972'>總聞曰此詩每章稱爾必雙舉牛羊而此章獨闕牛文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='5972:5995'>勢似不具識者更詳此士大夫檢校産畜料理生業者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='5995:6018'>也喪亂之後零替者多忽然見之人相與生驚故曰誰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='6018:6024'>謂爾無也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='6024:6027'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='6027:6036'>　詩總聞卷十一</span><br/>
